   Crump, W. Wesley; Stettler, Jason M.; Anderson, Chris D.; Harrison, Sarah; Meservey, Lindsey M.; Stevens, Mikel R., Brigham Young Univ, Dept Plant \& Wildlife Sci, Provo, UT 84602 USA.
